simnibs.msh.read_msh¶

simnibs.msh.read_msh(fn, m=None)¶

Reads a gmsh ‘.msh’ file

Parameters

  • fn (str) – File name

  • m (simnibs.msh.Msh (optional)) – Mesh structure to be overwritten. If unset, will create a new structure

Returns

msh – Mesh structure

Return type

simnibs.msh.Msh
